msgid "Part 2: Server Side Rendering"
msgstr ""

#: src/ssr/index.md:3
msgid ""
"As you read in the last chapter, there are some limitations to using client-"
"side rendered web applications. This second part of the book will discuss "
"how to use server-side rendering to overcome these limitations and get the "
"best performance and SEO out of your Leptos apps."
msgstr ""
